OL,3,CHuman rights groups criticise Troubles
OL,4,CBill 'lawfare' claims
OL,6,FGiving soldiers special impunity from
OL,7,Fhuman rights laws would destroy trust
OL,8,Fin the military and conceal
OL,9,Fwrongdoing, the Prime Minister has
OL,10,Fbeen told.
OL,12,FHuman rights groups have urged Sir
OL,13,FKeir Starmer to reject calls from
OL,14,Fretired senior military officers for a
OL,15,Flegal framework which would disapply
OL,16,Fthe European Convention on Human
OL,17,FRights and the Human Rights Act to
OL,18,Ftroops' actions while on active
OL,19,Fservice.
