OL,3,CHuman rights groups criticise Troubles
OL,4,CBill 'lawfare' claims
OL,6,FLast week, nine former four-star
OL,7,Fgenerals warned that soldiers' trust
OL,8,Fin the legal system is being eroded by
OL,9,F"lawfare", which they defined as "the
OL,10,Fuse of legal processes to fight
OL,11,Fpolitical or ideological battles".
OL,13,FThey claimed that "this lawfare is a
OL,14,Fdirect threat to national security"
OL,15,Fand risks weakening the operational
OL,16,Feffectiveness of the forces.
