OL,4,CBill 'lawfare' claims
OL,6,FIn a joint open letter to coincide
OL,7,Fwith Armistice Day which was published
OL,8,Fin The Times, the retired officials
OL,9,Fcriticised broadening interpretations
OL,10,Fof human rights law as well as "legal
OL,11,Factivism" behind the Troubles Bill.
OL,13,FThe legislation seeks to replace the
OL,14,Flast Conservative government's
OL,15,Fcontentious Legacy Act, which offered
OL,16,Fconditional immunity from prosecution
OL,17,Fto perpetrators in exchange for their
OL,18,Fco-operation with truth recovery
OL,19,Fmechanisms.
OL,26,@rD@`OUsD@IO]
