OL,3,CHuman rights groups criticise Troubles
OL,4,CBill 'lawfare' claims
OL,6,FThe new proposed legislation ditches
OL,7,Fthat controversial immunity provision
OL,8,Fand allows for the resumption of
OL,9,Fcriminal probes related to the
OL,10,FTroubles.
OL,12,FIt proposes a new-look Legacy
OL,13,FCommission that will take on criminal
OL,14,Finvestigations into Troubles deaths
OL,15,Fand a separate Independent Commission
OL,16,Ffor Information Retrieval, which will
OL,17,Fseek to provide answers to victims'
OL,18,Ffamilies in cases where criminal
OL,19,Fprosecutions are not considered
OL,20,Frealistic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
