OL,6,FIndividuals passing information to the
OL,7,Ftruth recovery body will be able to do
OL,8,Fso with an undertaking that the
OL,9,Faccount they provide cannot be used in
OL,10,Fcriminal proceedings against them.
OL,12,FThe generals said giving equivalent
OL,13,Fprotections to British soldiers as
OL,14,Fwell as other actors in the conflict
OL,15,Fwas "morally incoherent".
OL,17,FAmnesty International UK and the
OL,18,FCentre for Military Justice say the
OL,19,Fproposal to disapply the ECHR to
OL,20,Ftroops' actions is dangerous and would
OL,21,Fconceal wrongdoing.
