OL,6,FIn a letter to the Prime Minister seen
OL,7,Fby the PA news agency, they argue this
OL,8,Fwould breach domestic and
OL,9,Finternational law and leave families
OL,10,Fpermanently without answers by placing
OL,11,Fperpetrators beyond legal scrutiny and
OL,12,Fpreventing courts from examining
OL,13,Fserious crimes such as murder and
OL,14,Ftorture.
OL,16,FThey say hundreds of cases were shut
OL,17,Fdown by the Legacy Act, including at
OL,18,Fleast 225 serious criminal cases where
OL,19,Fthe victim was a member of the armed
OL,20,Fforces.
