OL,4,CBill 'lawfare' claims
OL,6,FGrainne Teggart, deputy director for
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland at Amnesty
OL,8,FInternational UK, said: "Attempts to
OL,9,Fpaint accountability as 'lawfare' are
OL,10,Fdeeply harmful and deliberately
OL,11,Fmisleading.
OL,13,F"Human rights protections uphold the
OL,14,Fvery basic principle that no-one is
OL,15,Fabove the law. Accountability
OL,16,Fstrengthens trust. Impunity destroys
OL,17,Fit."
