OL,6,FMs Teggart said the Belfast High Court
OL,7,Fhas already ruled that attempts to
OL,8,Fgrant a de facto amnesty for Troubles-
OL,9,Frelated offences are unlawful.
OL,11,FShe said: "We cannot ignore those most
OL,12,Faffected: victims and bereaved
OL,13,Ffamilies have spent decades seeking
OL,14,Ftruth and answers.
OL,16,F"Their trauma cannot be dismissed as
OL,17,Fan inconvenience to operational or
OL,18,Fpolitical interests.
