OL,6,F"Human rights protections are not a
OL,7,Fthreat; they are the safeguard against
OL,8,Fabuse of power."
OL,10,FEmma Norton, director at the Centre
OL,11,Ffor Military Justice, said the ECHR
OL,12,Fprotects UK forces fighting overseas
OL,13,Fand at home by ensuring they have
OL,14,Freasonably safe equipment, and by
OL,15,Fhaving investigations into alleged
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,18,FShe said: "A system that would protect
OL,19,Fwrongdoing is a threat to the
OL,20,Fmilitary, to public confidence and to
OL,21,Fthe rule of law.
