OL,6,F"The soldiers and military families we
OL,7,Fwork with want wrongdoing addressed,
OL,8,Fso that the many who served honourably
OL,9,Fare not tarnished by the actions of a
OL,10,Ffew.
OL,12,F"Service personnel understand that
OL,13,Fthey are both bound by, and protected
OL,14,Fby, the rule of law."
