OL,7,Fcriticised proposals to grant immunity
OL,8,Ffrom prosecution, which were central
OL,9,Fto the Legacy Act but were rejected by
OL,10,Fthe courts and are now being repealed.
OL,12,FDavid Crabbe, a veteran who served for
OL,13,F30 years in the Ulster Defence
OL,14,FRegiment and the Royal Irish Regiment
OL,15,Fduring the Troubles, said: "Op Banner
OL,16,Fveterans living in Northern Ireland
